SO ON YESTERDAY I SAW THIS LITTLE GIRL WALKING ALONE ON A BUSY AHS STREET THAT RUNS LIKE THE HIGHWAY. MAYBE IT IS A HIGHWAY IM NOT SURE IM NOT FROM GEORGIA. ANYWAYS I PASSED HER AND KEPT LOOKING BACK AND SAID “F” THAT TO MYSELF AND TURNED AROUND. AS I WAS TURNING I CALLED THE POLICE SO THEY CAN BE ON THE WAY. I WENT ON AND GOT OUT BECAUSE I WAS AFRAID SHE WOULD GET IN THE STREET. I HELD HER HAND AND TALKED TO HER TO SEE IF SHE KNEW WHERE SHE WAS GOING.. WHAT WAS HER NAME, HER MOMS NAME AND ETC… ANOTHER LADY STOP AND SAID SHE SAW HER WALKING TOO. SO THE POLICE CAME ABOUT FOUR OF THEM. I TALKED WITH THEM AS WELL AND LEFT EVERYTHING ELSE UP TO THEM. I EVENTUALLY LEFT THE SCENE BUT BEFORE I LEFT I EXCHANGED NUMBERS WITH THE LADY THAT CAME BACK AS WELL. SHE TEXTED ME AN HOUR LATER WITH THE PICTURE OF THE CHILD AND HER MOTHER. WHAT SCARE ME ABOUT THE SITUATION IS I MAY HAVE STOPPED AND SAVED HER FOR JUST THAT MOMENT CAUSE WHAT IF SHES STILL IN DANGER. PRAY FOR THE CHILDREN.
